Try executing this chunk by clicking the Run button within the chunk or by placing your cursor inside it and pressing Cmd+Shift+Enter.

library(ggplot2)
source("http://thegrantlab.org/misc/cdc.R")
View(cdc)
tail(cdc$weight,20)
 [1] 195 210 171 190 180 120 140 200 230 230 195 210
[13] 180 165 224 215 200 216 165 170
ggplot(cdc, aes(height, weight))+
  geom_point()+
  xlab("Height (inches)")+
  ylab("Weight (pounds)")

cor(cdc$weight,cdc$height)
[1] 0.5553222
height_m <- cdc$height * 0.0254
weight_kg <- cdc$weight * 0.454
bmi <- (weight_kg)/(height_m^2)
plot(cdc$height, bmi)

cor(cdc$height,bmi)
[1] 0.03251694
sum(bmi >= 30)
[1] 3897
plot(cdc[1:100,"weight"],cdc[1:100,"height"])

sum(bmi>=30)
[1] 3897
obese <- cdc[bmi>=30,]
length(obese[,1])
[1] 3897
male_obese <- sum(obese$gender == "m")
male_obese
[1] 1961
